IBA_efficiency_data_analysis_and_visualization

2024-03-13

This document is one of the R scripts accompanying paper “High-throughput biodiversity surveying sheds new light on the brightest of insect taxa” - Iwaszkiewicz-Eggebrecht et al. 2024

It contains: - Basic stats summarizing metabarcoding results - Summary of known Swedish fauna (DynTaxa data) - Matching of species names between metabarcoding and known Swedish fauna - Calulating percentages of species recovered by metabarcoding methods and plotting results
